Borrowing her life.

118
00:11:23,999 --> 00:11:26,593
I'm dedicating the book to her.
She's pleased.

119
00:11:35,511 --> 00:11:36,876
Do you exhibit?

120
00:11:36,946 --> 00:11:39,847
Sometimes. I have a thing next year.

121
00:11:45,855 --> 00:11:47,186
Portraits?

122
00:11:49,258 --> 00:11:51,852
- Of who?
- Strangers.

123
00:11:54,830 --> 00:11:58,322
How do your strangers feel
about you stealing their lives?

124
00:11:58,501 --> 00:11:59,900
Borrowing.

125
00:12:01,470 --> 00:12:02,835
