127
00:12:07,376 --> 00:12:09,435
And you're a sloucher. Sit up.

128
00:12:16,085 --> 00:12:17,552
You didn't find it obscene?

129
00:12:17,620 --> 00:12:19,212
- What?
- The book.

130
00:12:20,556 --> 00:12:22,683
I thought it was accurate.

131
00:12:23,325 --> 00:12:24,792
