133
00:12:27,730 --> 00:12:29,163
In what way?

134
00:12:29,632 --> 00:12:32,829
- You wrote it.
- You read it till 4:00.

135
00:12:33,168 --> 00:12:36,228
Don't raise your eyebrows.
It makes you look smug.

136
00:12:44,547 --> 00:12:47,812
- But you did like it?
- Yes, but I could go off it.

137
00:12:54,256 --> 00:12:55,587
Stand up.

138
00:13:01,864 --> 00:13:03,695
Any criticisms?

139
00:13:05,301 --> 00:13:06,859
