143
00:13:13,976 --> 00:13:16,706
- You like aquariums.
- Fish are therapeutic.

144
00:13:16,779 --> 00:13:19,145
- Hang out in aquariums, do you?
- When I can.

145
00:13:19,214 --> 00:13:21,045
