147
00:13:33,095 --> 00:13:34,426
Come here.

148
00:13:51,714 --> 00:13:53,375
You're beautiful.

149
00:14:01,056 --> 00:14:03,388
I don't kiss strange men.

150
00:14:03,792 --> 00:14:05,282
Neither do I.

151
00:15:16,632 --> 00:15:19,294
Do you and this Alice live together?

152
00:15:24,106 --> 00:15:25,437
Yes.

153
00:15:36,985 --> 00:15:38,384
Are you married?

154
00:15:38,454 --> 00:15:39,785
Yes.

155
00:15:40,022 --> 00:15:42,616
- No. Yes.
- Which?

156
00:15:42,958 --> 00:15:44,619
Separated.

157
00:15:45,260 --> 00:15:46,887
- Do you have any children?
- No.

158
00:15:46,962 --> 00:15:49,954
- Would you like some?
- Yes, but not today.

159
00:15:50,699 --> 00:15:53,031
Would Alice like children?

160
00:15:54,069 --> 00:15:55,593
She's too young.

161
00:15:56,805 --> 00:16:00,297
She works in a café near here.
She's coming to meet me.

162
00:16:01,076 --> 00:16:02,475
Quite soon.

163
00:16:05,147 --> 00:16:07,479
