164
00:16:08,617 --> 00:16:11,450
- You're judgmental.
- You're devious.

165
00:16:11,520 --> 00:16:15,217
I'm not wasting her time.
She's completely lovable.

166
00:16:15,290 --> 00:16:17,121
And completely unleavable.

167
00:16:17,192 --> 00:16:21,219
