Can I use your loo?

184
00:17:40,108 --> 00:17:42,042
Sure. Just through there.

185
00:17:49,618 --> 00:17:50,915
She is beautiful.

186
00:17:50,986 --> 00:17:53,045
- I've got to see you.
- No.

187
